        <h3><strong>Core Features and Capabilities</strong></h3>
        <p>
          The platform recently deployed 78 production updates, delivering a comprehensive project-level scoring and leaderboard system. These enhancements include infinite scroll functionality for the web interface and numerous improvements to analytics accuracy.
        </p>
        <p>
          At its core, X Bot automatically tracks every X user mentioning your project and syncs posts directly into Telegram. The system captures engagement metrics across platforms, then gamifies community support through intelligent scoring mechanisms that reward active participants.
        </p>
        <p>
          Building on this foundation, recent updates introduced multi-account tracking capabilities. Projects can now monitor multiple X handles simultaneously, segment data by account, and generate separate leaderboards for different campaign initiatives—making it easier to run parallel marketing efforts.
        </p>
        <h3><strong>Key Benefits and Advantages</strong></h3>
