        </p>
        <h3><strong>Getting Started with X Bot</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Implementation requires only four simple commands in your Telegram group. Add @BWS_X_Bot to your group as an admin, then call /set_project_name with your project name, /add_mentions with your X account, and /recreate to initialize tracking.
        </p>
